traces = []
def tracer(old_state, input, new_state):
    traces.append((old_state, input, new_state))
    return None
s = SampleObject()
s.setTrace(tracer)
s.go1()
self.assertEqual(traces, [('begin', 'go1', 'middle')])
s.go2()
self.assertEqual(traces, [('begin', 'go1', 'middle'), ('middle', 'go2', 'end')]
    )
s.setTrace(None)
s.back()
self.assertEqual(traces, [('begin', 'go1', 'middle'), ('middle', 'go2', 'end')]
    )
s.go2()
self.assertEqual(traces, [('begin', 'go1', 'middle'), ('middle', 'go2', 'end')]
    )
